---
title: Zesty Honey-Glazed Chicken & Garlic Greens with Almonds & Chilli Flakes
description: Fresh, fast, and oh-so-flavourful! Tonight, juicy chicken meets a zesty glaze of lemon, honey and oregano. Add some vibrant greens, topped off with a kick of chilli and the perfect crunch of almonds. Healthy never tasted so delicious!

